function BookingForm(){
    return(
        <bookingform>
            <form>
                <label htmlFor="res-date">Choose date</label>
                <input type="date" id="res-date"/>

                <label htmlFor="res-time">Choose time</label>
                <select id="res-time">
                    <option>17:00</option>
                    <option>18:00</option>
                    <option>19:00</option>
                    <option>20:00</option>
                    <option>21:00</option>
                    <option>22:00</option>
                </select>
            </form>
        </bookingform>
    )
}

export default BookingForm
